  <thing id="bgParenDra" name="Parentage - Draconic Adoption" description="You were adopted by a dragon. What sort of dragon was it, and how did it treat you?{br}{i}Associated Skills: {/i}Arcana{br}{i}Associated Languages: {/i}Draconic" compset="Background" uniqueness="unique">
