    </thing>
  <thing id="bgParenIll" name="Parentage - Ill-Omened" description="When you were born, the moon turned red or birds died mid-flight and fell from the sky. Do the omens still strike you? Have you learned to read them?{br}{i}Associated Skills: {/i}Arcana, Religion" compset="Background" uniqueness="unique">
