  <thing id="bgParenImp" name="Parentage - Impoverished" description="Your parents were dirt poor and couldn&apos;t provide you with a thing. Did you resolve to do better for yourself or for your parents?{br}{i}Associated Skills: {/i}Endurance, Streetwise" compset="Background" uniqueness="unique">
