  <thing id="bgParenMon" name="Parentage - Monk Business" description="The quiet people of a monastery raised you and taught you their ways. Are you still in touch with the monks, and what philosophies did they espouse?{br}{i}Associated Skills: {/i}Heal, History" compset="Background" uniqueness="unique">
